text: Apakah paypal bakal di blokir sama kominfo? jangan dong pacck, dana kenakalan saya jangan direnggut☹️
en_text: Will Paypal be blocked with the Ministry of Communication and Information? Don't pacck, my delinquency funds don't be snatched away

text: Paypal resmi tidak bisa lagi di akses di Indonesia, perusahaan yang bergerak di bidang jasa keuangan digital yang bermarkas di Amerika serikat tersebut,di kabarkan belum terdaftar di situs resmi kementerian Kominfo RI, di Indonesia, Paypal juga bekerjasama dengan Traveloka
en_text: Paypal officially can no longer be accessed in Indonesia, a company engaged in the field of digital financial services based in the United States, reportedly not yet registered at the official website of the Ministry of Communication and Information, in Indonesia, Paypal also cooperates with Traveloka

text: Selain Amazon dan Alibaba, kementerian Kominfo RI juga membekukan sementara waktu Paypal, karena pihak pengelola platform jasa keuangan digital tersebut, belum terdaftar di kementerian Kominfo RI.sedangkan Apple pay dan Shopee pay, sudah terdaftar di kementerian Kominfo RI
en_text: Besides Amazon and Alibaba, the Ministry of Communication and Information of the Republic of Indonesia also temporarily frozen Paypal, because the manager of the digital financial services platform, has not been registered with the Ministry of Communication and Information.
